document_title: Aortic valve stenosis: Symptoms, causes and treatments
subsection_name: hep-van-dong-mach-chu.json_4_Dangerous complications of aortic valve stenosis
subsection_content:
Aortic valve stenosis is one of the most dangerous heart valve diseases. The disease can lead to many dangerous complications such as:
Heart failure.; Endocarditis; Arrhythmia; Stroke; Blood clot; Dead
